description: Bakhu Holdings, Corp. focuses on the production, manufacturing, and sale of cannabis-related byproducts for medical, food additive, and recreational use in the United States and the Caribbean. The company was formerly known as Planet Resources, Corp. and changed its name to Bakhu Holdings, Corp. in May 2009. Bakhu Holdings, Corp. was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Long Beach, California.
ceo: Mr. Juan Carlos Garcia La Sienra Garcia
